- Introduction to web application testing  

 Defensive Security (Blue Team Basics)
- Log analysis fundamentals  
- Identifying suspicious activity  
- Basic incident response concepts  
- Introduction to security monitoring  

 Cryptography & Security Concepts
- Hashing and encryption basics  
- Password security and cracking concepts  
- Secure communication principles  

 Practical Hands-On Skills
- Solving real-world cybersecurity labs and challenges  
- Performing basic penetration testing workflows  
- Analyzing system and network behavior  
- Developing problem-solving mindset for security tasks  
